Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{=14}---- Dialogue
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.65,0:00:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{=6}Look who we have here.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.36,0:00:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been expecting you,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.66,0:00:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the legendary Horu—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.57,0:00:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.08,0:00:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you would prefer Takanashi Hoshino{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a change of plans.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.88,0:00:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to once again extend an offer to you,\nthe wielder of the strongest Mystic in Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.01,0:00:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't screw with me! {Let the Ojisan say fuck? --ML}{perchance -rapid}{would -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.89,0:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, now. No need to get angry.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.76,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I am extending an offer you cannot possibly refuse.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.35,0:00:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I assure you, you will find\nthis proposal quite fascinating.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.17,0:02:36.01,Default,,800,0,0,,We end today's segment\nwith a report from the Abydos district.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.59,0:02:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite the recent explosion,\nthe desert shows no signs of change.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.52,0:02:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This concludes our news for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.77,0:02:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see you again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How did things end up like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.46,0:03:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What I meant was, how many more\nshould I write, President Hina?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.14,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've written about two hundred so far, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you would write a thousand?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.93,0:03:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What I meant was that I was\nso ashamed I {\i1}could{\i0} write a thousand!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Less talking, more writing.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.90,0:03:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, have you met\nHoshino from Abydos before?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.16,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I did research on her\nwhile I was in intelligence,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but this was my first time\nmeeting her in person.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.67,0:03:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You sounded like you knew her well,\nso I presumed you had met her before.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.42,0:03:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A true elite. A prodigy by all standards.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.47,0:04:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The intelligence division's analysis two years ago\nlisted her as a potential threat to Gehenna.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.18,0:04:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She certainly didn't give me that impression.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.64,0:04:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako, you should refrain from\nmaking judgments based on appearances.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.61,0:04:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.94,0:04:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She really {\i1}did{\i0} seem like\na completely different person.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.95,0:04:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, she was extremely aggressive,\nspecialising in assault tactics.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.41,0:04:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on the reports, she struck me as a rough,\nyet dangerously sharp individual.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's set her past aside for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.63,0:04:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Had we carelessly engaged Abydos,\nwe would have lost more than half our forces.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.34,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All because you jumped the gun, Ako.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.13,0:04:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read their profiles,\nand they didn't seem capable of that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.10,0:04:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She did just fall off the grid one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.14,0:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At some point, intelligence may have\nstopped viewing her as a threat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.48,0:04:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're curious, I recommend\ndigging through those old reports.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ako. Those letters won't write themselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.41,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.20,0:05:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You were still in Abydos after all this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.09,0:05:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, where should I put this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.63,0:05:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, the crime against calligraphy\nAru poured all her talent into.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just chuck it in the bin.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the thing she made for calligraphy class, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.90,0:05:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess she may wanna keep that anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.24,0:05:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.32,0:05:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so obvious she doesn't wanna move.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.03,0:05:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, but the Prefects\nwill be swarming this place soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.29,0:05:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And since we messed up,\nthe client'll want a piece of us too.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No sense crying over spilt milk.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.25,0:05:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of enemies, our little dispute\nwith Abydos ended up unresolved, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.88,0:06:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What else were we supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.47,0:06:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They fought alongside us. We couldn't just\nturn around and stab them in the back!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.60,0:06:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.10,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Outlaws have to know when to let go of the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.10,0:06:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So chin up and say goodbye to this old place.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kayoko{**-chan}, what do we do with this?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.69,0:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we really need that?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.74,0:06:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we do!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.32,0:06:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We have smartphones, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about convenience. It's about atmosphere! {VIBES --ik}{### that was my first thought, but figured it'd be too memey :(}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.70,0:06:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this retro design {\i1}just right{\i0} for an outlaw's office?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.29,0:06:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think so, yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.96,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's cool.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd understand, Haruka!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.97,0:06:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a step back. It's only a brief detour.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how dire things seem now,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.47,0:06:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be back in this office one day. Just you wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.73,0:06:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.98,0:06:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're real, bona fide outlaws!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:59.19,0:06:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,shenan,{\alpha&HFF&}Because we're real, bona fide outlaws!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.19,0:06:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,shenan,{\clip(m 1220 899 l 1920 899 1920 1080 1077 1080)}Because we're real, bona fide outlaws!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're Problem Solver 68!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, we finally bid this place adieu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.54,0:07:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.66,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't pay last month's rent,\nso they want us out today.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we're pitching tents tonight!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.26,0:07:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.68,0:07:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.60,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last box.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.11,0:07:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Aru{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.40,0:07:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the first time we've camped out.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just going back to how things used to be.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.74,0:07:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Going back...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're not going back!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're moving up!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, where to?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not like we have anywhere {\i1}to{\i0} go.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go back to Gehenna?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.34,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving somewhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.68,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you were... Sunaookami Shiroko{**-chan}, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.48,0:08:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not here for a rematch, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.85,0:08:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.94,0:08:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was biking in the area\nand happened to spot you.
Comment: 10,0:08:24.07,0:08:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{Mesugaki noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.20,0:08:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.54,0:08:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A-About the other day...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for helping us!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And also, about the ramen shop...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.22,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's different.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.19,0:09:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But you do seem like you're sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe us one. How's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.40,0:09:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the ones who left that bag, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1800,2300,0.5,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}I-I have no idea what you mean!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.95,0:09:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about a bag filled with money!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I've never even heard of such a thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.00,0:09:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aru{**-chan}, you know you gave the game away\nby mentioning the money, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.25,0:09:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You stole that money\nwhen you robbed the bank, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.22,0:09:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not so desperate that we'd claim\nanother gang's spoils for ourselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Outlaws have standards, too! {omg Sniper TF2 --ML}{### I almost wanna put "professionals" now} {Be polite. Be efficient --ik}{we're not common criminals, we're outlaws -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.06,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look who's sassy now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I went ahead and delivered the bag to the boss.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will you go?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.86,0:09:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever there's clients in need of\nProblem Solver 68's services!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aru{**-chan}, we should get going.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.83,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.62,0:10:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find a place to camp tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.50,0:10:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want to?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.26,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I have no intention of acting\nall chummy with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.68,0:10:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,An outlaw, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I see you again?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.06,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, if that ramen shop ever opens again,\nmaybe we'll meet there again someday?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.11,0:10:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.27,0:10:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's time for us to venture out ourselves!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.11,0:10:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Out where?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.90,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Into the sunset!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still the middle of the day.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the details. Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.96,0:10:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to visit, boss.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, don't worry 'bout me.\n'Tis but a scratch.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.55,0:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, that was a mighty fine blast.\nSure glad no one 'sides me was caught up in it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.81,0:11:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your restaurant...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.77,0:11:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Sorry Serika{**-chan}, but I can't really\nkeep you around anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about that, boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.70,0:11:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.03,0:11:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinkin' 'bout closing up shop either way.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.45,0:11:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The closing date just came knockin' a bit early is all.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.58,0:11:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You were going to close?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.87,0:11:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'see, I received an eviction notice a while back.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.42,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A-An eviction notice? That shouldn't be possible!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.30,0:11:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Our school owns all the buildings in the Abydos district.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.88,0:11:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you girls didn't know, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.26,0:11:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The buildings and the land stopped bein' the property\nof the student council a few years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're within the Abydos district.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika{**-chan}, did you know about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.40,0:11:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is the first I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.36,0:11:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean there's another debt\nAbydos had to pay off?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know about this, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who does the property belong to now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.74,0:12:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be the Kaiser Corporation again?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.96,0:12:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That name {\i1}does{\i0} ring a bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.00,0:12:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But sorry, I just can't remember it well.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.05,0:12:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We should probably investigate this further.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane{**-chan}, let me help out, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.93,0:12:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too. I'll help however I can.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.64,0:12:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry 'bout that. Seems things\nhave only gotten more complicated.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.60,0:12:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\nThis is our problem, not yours.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.19,0:12:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But enough about that.\nDon't you dare retire on me, boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.65,0:12:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.57,0:12:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.95,0:12:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's somethin' under the bed.\nMind pulling it out real quick?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.25,0:12:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anythin' about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.38,0:12:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you {\i1}could{\i0} say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.96,0:12:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.04,0:12:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, y'see, Shiroko{**-chan} came by\nand dropped it off earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.76,0:13:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Said she found it in front of\nwhat little's left of my restaurant.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.72,0:13:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So obviously I got curious and opened it up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.68,0:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And wouldn't ya know, it's stuffed full of cash!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.06,0:13:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Guessin' this ain't just a tip for good service, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.52,0:13:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who knows, maybe it is?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.44,0:13:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's from a well-meaning stranger!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.02,0:13:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I bet they would want you\nto use it to rebuild your restaurant!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.32,0:13:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm sure whoever left this behind\nwas touched by your ramen!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.24,0:13:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'all gotta be kiddin' me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.08,0:13:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's true, I can't even tell ya\nhow happy that makes me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.17,0:13:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want in life is to see my hungry customers\neatin' their fill of delicious ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.17,0:13:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what kept me goin' all these years!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.42,0:13:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all dying to have your ramen again.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.26,0:13:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So hurry and get better,\nand then rebuild your restaurant!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.51,0:13:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And once that's done,\nyou'd better hire me again, boss.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.19,0:13:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment I'm back on my feet,\nI'll feed ya all the ramen you can stomach!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.74,0:14:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya, Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.78,0:14:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather's nice.\nOut for a nap on the roof today?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.46,0:14:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.17,0:14:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of taking a little break myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.17,0:14:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been here for a good while now, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.18,0:14:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.93,0:14:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta be honest, at first I thought\nyou were just another weirdo.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.31,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out I'm pretty reliable after all, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.14,0:14:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please. You're all over the place,\nand you're constantly playing catch-up.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But y'know...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.32,0:14:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Task Force seems\na lot happier now with you around.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.61,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take credit for that. That's because\nthey got a clear direction for the future now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you could be right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.08,0:14:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika{**-chan} doesn't try to do\neverything on her own anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.54,0:14:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane{**-chan} doesn't look so down all the time, I guess?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.84,0:15:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonomi{**-chan} laughs for herself now,\nnot just to make the others happy. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.47,0:15:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And as for Shiroko{**-chan}...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.05,0:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's breathing easier now.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.14,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing your best, too.\nEveryone trusts in you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.60,0:15:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to give them the chance\nto live a normal life.{###}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.20,0:15:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they're able to keep smiling.{###}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.37,0:15:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I have to move on.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.71,0:15:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.46,0:15:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I feel a lot better after hearing you say that.\nNow I can really enjoy my nap!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.17,0:15:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought you were finally\nbeing serious for once.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.23,0:15:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Arona.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.44,0:16:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where did my strawberry cake go?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And my banana cake?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.57,0:16:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this my punishment for trying to eat two at once?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.45,0:16:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Arona?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.95,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one bite would have been enough...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.66,0:16:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to bring some cake next time.\nStrawberry and banana, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you had to see that.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.17,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But thank you! I look forward to them!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.05,0:16:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.01,0:16:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something I wanted to ask.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.09,0:16:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you look into the Kaiser Corporation for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.14,0:16:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kaiser Corporation?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.64,0:16:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're up to no good\nin the Abydos desert.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.31,0:16:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.94,0:16:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else you'd like me\nto look into in the meantime?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino's...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.98,0:16:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.78,0:16:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.70,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to figure this out on my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.49,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm her teacher, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, if you say so.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.33,0:17:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. You're always a big help.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.13,0:17:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.26,0:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm both the talented systems administrator\nof the Shittim Chest {\i1}and{\i0} its main OS, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And above all,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.01,0:17:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2340,3220,0.4,\c&HFDFDFD&\3c&HFDFDFD&\4c&HFDFDFD&)}I'm your helpful personal assistant!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.31,0:17:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then. I wonder if everyone's back.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.69,0:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.82,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How was the boss doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.86,0:17:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He was doing great, in both health and spirit!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.62,0:17:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'll rebuild his restaurant soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.83,0:17:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.54,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.87,0:17:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We've actually run into another problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.30,0:17:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just about to dive into it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.26,0:17:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply put, it seems that Abydos High\ndoes not own the land in this area.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.01,0:18:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Doesn't the land within\na school district belong to the school?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.73,0:18:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the boss, even the building Shiba Seki\nwas in doesn't belong to us anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.74,0:18:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know for sure,\nbut the boss said it was a few years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So who owns it now?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kaiser Corporation.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.50,0:18:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't start just recently.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.08,0:18:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This had been going on since before we ever met\nProblem Solver 68 or the Helmet Gang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.92,0:18:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been dancing to the tune\nof Kaiser Corporation all along.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.34,0:18:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,God, now I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.59,0:18:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We won't know for sure\nuntil we get to the bottom of this.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We may be jumping to conclusions.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.69,0:18:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like I can never get enough sleep\nno matter how many naps I take these days.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.36,0:18:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm just getting old.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.99,0:18:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.03,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, take a look at that!\nDoesn't that cloud look kinda like a whale?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.62,0:18:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.53,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's right there! The big one!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.45,0:19:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see it from all the way back there.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.25,0:19:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come closer. I promise I won't bite.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.46,0:19:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop pulling me!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.46,0:19:10.75,Alt,,0,0,0,,Come on now!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me? We're in the middle of\na serious conversation!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time for—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.38,0:19:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, why don't we\ntake a look too, Serika{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.47,0:19:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You, too, Nonomi{**-senpai}?\nWhat's going on with everyone?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean that cloud right there?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.08,0:19:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say it looks more like a dolphin than a whale.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.52,0:19:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Hoshino{**-senpai} means\nthe cloud above that one. Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.94,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When you put it that way,\nthe one under it does kinda look like a dolphin.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.15,0:19:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess that makes the one\nunderneath that one a jellyfish{Can't Swim in the Night}?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.16,0:19:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember jellyfish\nlooking quite like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.70,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There may be some kinds that do.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that we're on the topic,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.42,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,let's all go to the aquarium together!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.92,0:19:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't found anything yet anyway, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.13,0:19:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Moping around with a frown on your face\nwon't change anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.85,0:20:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd rather we smile while we wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.86,0:20:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, Serika{**-chan}, there's\ntons of jellyfish over at the aquarium.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.49,0:20:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so nice to look at.\nAll wiggly and squiggly!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.20,0:20:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, won't you indulge li'l ol' me just this once?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.91,0:20:23.54,Alt,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine, I'll go. Happy?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.54,0:20:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. A break every once in a while\nmay be just what we need.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.54,0:20:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Breaks are important!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming too, right, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.83,0:20:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.84,0:20:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "huh"? You busy?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.25,0:20:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe we need a teacher to chaperone us.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.09,0:20:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.51,0:20:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, let's all go together!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.31,0:20:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{=15}It's gonna be so much fun!

